                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040704-54-victim545 t18040704-54-viclabel303"></join>. And a</p>
               <p>Third Count. Charging it to be the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18040704-54-victim547" type="victimName">
                     Joyce 
                     Dale
                  <interp inst="t18040704-54-victim547" type="surname" value="Dale"></interp>
